[{"index":1,"title":"笑依然，夜如故","content":"1楼敬百度","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-04 20:36","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"好吧我承认有时自己也看不下去了，不过可怜可怜六年级小同学吧。随便怎么称呼。","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-04 20:39","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"用的是《钗头凤》的词牌（以葛琪琪的角度写的）<br>       <br>     欢声荡，昔难忘，欢笑依然景犹在；<br>     昨日雨，窗外云，<br>     时光虽短，回忆却长，<br>     念.念.念。<br>    <br>     花亦落，人亦错，夜色如故人何在；<br>     月光寒，星光残，<br>     寂夜长风，故人心声，<br>     寒.寒.寒<br>\u0018","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-04 21:05","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"诗意：<br>     曾经的欢笑声再次在我耳边响起，昔时的旧景仍是难以忘却。昨天下的雨，窗外飘的云，都似曾相识。那段校园时光虽然短暂，但回忆却很漫长，令人念想。<br>     花又一次无情的落了，此时才明白从先做错的过往。夜色仍旧阑珊，旧时的人却已不知去向。月光给人以一种彻骨的寒，星光却依然灿烂。寂静夜里的长风，就像是我的心声。愈加心寒。\u0018","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-04 21:12","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"难道就没人看吗<br>    好吧，自己顶下<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/tsj/t_0003.gif\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\"><br>","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-05 10:20","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"这词用的是《长相思》的词牌（以上官帅的角度写的）<br>    <br>        兰花落，<br>        行人过，<br>        谁人见过少年愁，<br>        明眸藏迷茫。<br><br>        刀刃落，<br>        擦身过，<br>        星沉月落人飘坠，<br>        相逢终有期。<br><br>","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-05 11:08","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":7,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"诗意：<br>兰花飘落，行人匆匆而过，又有谁看见了少年的愁苦？明亮的眸子里隐藏着淡淡的迷茫。<br>一瞬间，刀刃落下，擦身而过。那一刻，星星沉下，月亮落下，人们纷纷坠下漩涡。终会相逢。","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-05 11:12","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":8,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"抱歉可能不太押韵。偶还是六年级学生。<br>大家说下一个写谁好","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-05 11:13","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":9,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/jd/j_0006.gif\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\">","author":"冰恋婉儿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f33ca355.Y6fl0iKisswX91GbqTEzvw?t=1681363143&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-06 08:42","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/gjlslsx/pic/item/6fb64cd97d8e594d10df9b42.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":10,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"谢谢<br>    词牌：《谒金门》（以毛小蒙的角度写的）<br>   <br>     热血情，<br>　　点亮少年模样。 <br>　　天生我材必有用， <br>　　笑容依然存。<br>　　<br>     身世迷离可叹， <br>　　天赋异常可惊 。<br>　　穿越时空显本领， <br>　　寂夜不再凉。<br><br><br> 写的有点匆忙，但还看得下去，就发了<br>   <br>\u0018","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-06 10:15","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":11,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"诗意：<br>   一腔热血，照亮了少年的容貌。老天已经生下了他，就也赐予了他惊人的天赋，纯洁的笑容仍然会挂在他的脸上。<br>   身世的迷离使人感叹，天赋的异常令人惊讶。穿越时空展现自己的本领，有了它，寂夜也不在空凉 。<br><br>   10楼格式发错了。","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-06 10:22","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":12,"title":"回复：笑依然，夜如故","content":"至此就over了，希望大家多支持。","author":"天使PK棒棒糖","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.17ca2f26.qJ5AXY64KVcf4EsbJPLvxQ?t=1601301279&fr=pb","date":"2011-11-06 13:17","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null}]